## üí° Usage Tips

### CSS Example:

```css
.post-list li::before {
  content: '‚ä≥'; /* swap with any above */
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: #999;
}
```

### Visual Strategy:

* Use `‚ü°`, `‚ä≥`, or `‚ó¶` for high-information posts
* Use `‚Üí`, `‚ñ∏`, or `‚Ä∫` for lists and sequences
* Use `‚ú∂` or `‚≠ë` sparingly for standout or featured posts

